                <h3 class="subheading">Electronics & Connectivity</h3>
                <p><span class="font-weight-700">Display</span></p>
                <p>The F 450 GS comes with a large <span class="font-weight-700">6.5-inch TFT color display </span>as standard. It's bright, readable in multiple lighting conditions, and operated via a multi-controller on the left handlebar. Two screen layouts come standard: </p>
